title: Thom Hartmann Program - January 09 2014
description:
January 09, 2014
The Thom Hartmann Program 


Hour One: Is Chris Christie's car out of control?  Congressman Mark Pocan (D-WI, 2nd District)

Hour Two: Chris Christie's Nixon moment - Mike Papantonio, Ring of Fire Radio / Plus, Geeky Science - Global warming releases unknown diseases?

Hour Three: What does socialism mean to you? - Kshama Sawant, Seattle City Council
